      </div>

      <div class="span5 intro">
        <p>Sockethub is a polyglot (speaking many different protocols and APIs) messaging service for social and other interactive messaging applications. It assists web app developers by providing server-independent, server-side functionality - which gives the application greater autonomy. It can be used as a tool for many different types of applications, large and small.</p>

        <p class="donations"><span>Support Sockethub Development</span><p>
